Day 2: Text Formatting & Links

Today you'll learn how to format text and create hyperlinks.

1. Bold Text
<b> Tag

Makes text bold visually.

<b>Java Developer</b>

Output:
Java Developer

2. Strong Text
<strong> Tag

Makes text important and usually bold.

<strong>Important Notice</strong>

Output:
Important Notice

Interview Question

Difference between <b> and <strong>?

<b> → Only bold appearance.
<strong> → Indicates important content (semantic meaning).

Prefer <strong> in modern HTML.

3. Italic Text
<i> Tag
<i>Learning HTML</i>

Output:
Learning HTML

4. Emphasized Text
<em> Tag
<em>Read Carefully</em>

Output:
Read Carefully

Difference
<i> → Visual italic.
<em> → Adds emphasis/importance.
5. Highlight Text
